{"tid":1012004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還是台灣好！台商狂讚中國 卻狼狽逃回來...","createTime":"2019-02-07T08:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T08:10:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"341f5ec7e5eee7cab28f9b8a92818f4ad7750ac6","tid":1012004,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"還是台灣好！台商狂讚中國 卻狼狽逃回來...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2692313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2692313&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9ee2027b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2692313&h=953afe9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2692313</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕農曆春節期間，不少在外打拚的台灣人，也返家過年團聚。桃園市議員王浩宇今在臉書分享一名在中國工作的友人，對方每次春節返鄉總當眾人面稱讚上海進步、數落台灣，「但今年過年，他沒有要回去中國了。」<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇在文中表示，該名台商先前過年回來愛講「上海多麼進步、台灣多麼落後」，並指對方抱怨回台不習慣、鼓勵他們去中國賺錢，「說自己在中國的生意多麼成功，跟當地官員的關係多好多好」。<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇在文中指出，不過，「今年過年，他沒有要回去中國了」，並解釋友人經營的汽車零件廠，因中美貿易戰、中國內需緊縮與出口衰退，「過去半年幾乎是訂單歸零」，還稱對方的教會因中國政策關閉，「連聚會的自由都沒有了」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">王浩宇在文中提到，友人在幾乎無路可走下，「幾乎是逃回台灣」，並宣稱其廠房、存款似被中國當地主管投資的官員合夥人侵吞。王也在文中提及，中國不少建設新、效率快，但「建築在獨裁政府的違法迫遷、迫害人權下」，加上「貪腐嚴重」，部分建設若遇天災出狀況，政府選擇封鎖消息。</span><br />\n<br />\n王浩宇在文中引述，友人這次回來，感慨在中國時常得戴口罩上班、沒有一天進城不塞車、怕得罪官員被找碴，生活過得「提心吊膽」、「緊張兮兮」。「而台灣終究是自己的家，就算落後點、就算窮了點，至少空氣是自由的，『看久了，還是台灣好』。」"},{"pid":"4bf54b1814d5bf4306cabfba91c89c5c26606b53","tid":1012004,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190694a5a330a3c6936f59071c935e599438fd3d","tid":1012004,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f717821b4b2b1b74502b3780ac134d17f02a30","tid":1012004,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"好馬不吃回頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f62488711dbb52002d2de418c3a69e4f585f972","tid":1012004,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會比人舉報下呢位人兄呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e42e6c7316156656a1a44db71e05f3bf7c3a7d","tid":1012004,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dec2b3b270fd5ca67a0d6fba5b3b8f3fb3684c","tid":1012004,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c0c691a39d48bcaafbc97e9d61b183ac1d73e7","tid":1012004,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"台狗大多數真係弱智"},{"pid":"c13706943ea0158f85eb0bf173ee78bb5c84b695","tid":1012004,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1012974/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1012974/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n奶錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18592baa4295c13647de37f70e8e0459a925fed8","tid":1012004,"uid":89530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"牆頭草，商人就係商人，有錢賺，食屎都制"},{"pid":"9d0e85d79a779ee81359257c6e4fc914f52e87af","tid":1012004,"uid":3241,"li